@startuml proxy-auto-heal-sequence
!include _standard-style.puml

title Proxy Auto-Heal — Health Coordinator Self-Recovery

participant "Health\nCoordinator" as HC #F5F5F5
participant "Proxydetox\n(port 3128)" as PD #E8F4FD
participant "LLM Proxy\n(port 12435)" as LLM #F3E5F5
participant "launchctl" as LC #FFF2E6
participant "tmux\nStatus Line" as TM #E8F5E8

== Normal Operation (proxy healthy) ==

HC -> PD: TCP probe port 3128
PD --> HC: connected (< 100ms)
HC -> PD: curl -x 127.0.0.1:3128\nhttps://api.github.com
PD --> HC: HTTP 200
HC -> HC: proxy_running = true\nproxy_functional = true
TM -> HC: GET /health/state
HC --> TM: P:ON (green)

== Network Change (e.g. VPN disconnect) ==

note over PD #FFEBEE
  PAC URL unreachable on new network.
  Proxydetox enters broken state —
  port open but requests fail.
end note

HC -> PD: TCP probe port 3128
PD --> HC: connected (port alive)
HC -> PD: curl -x 127.0.0.1:3128\nhttps://api.github.com
PD --> HC: **connection error** (broken)

HC -> HC: proxy_functional = **false**\nproxyEnabledByUser = true\n→ auto-heal triggered

|||

== Auto-Heal ==

HC -> LC: launchctl kickstart -k\ngui/501/com.coding.proxydetox
LC -> PD: restart daemon
LC --> HC: exit 0

note over HC #E8F5E8
  Wait 2s for daemon
  to re-initialize
end note

HC -> PD: TCP probe port 3128
PD --> HC: connected
HC -> PD: curl -x 127.0.0.1:3128\nhttps://api.github.com
PD --> HC: HTTP 200

HC -> HC: proxy_running = true\nproxy_functional = true

|||

== LLM Proxy Recovery (immediate re-probe) ==

note over HC #FFEBEE
  Proxy healed but semantic_ok
  may still be false — LLM proxy
  holds stale HTTP connections.
end note

HC -> LLM: POST /api/complete\n{"process":"health","messages":[...]}
LLM --> HC: **fetch failed** (stale conn)

HC -> HC: semantic_ok = false\n+ recent proxy heal\n→ LLM proxy restart triggered

HC -> LC: launchctl kickstart -k\ngui/501/com.coding.llm-cli-proxy
LC -> LLM: restart daemon
LC --> HC: exit 0

note over HC #E8F5E8
  Wait 2s for LLM proxy
  to re-initialize
end note

HC -> LLM: POST /api/complete\n{"process":"health","messages":[...]}
LLM --> HC: {"content":"OK"}

HC -> HC: semantic_ok = true
TM -> HC: GET /health/state
HC --> TM: P:ON (green)\nLLM:● (green)

note over HC #FFFACD
  Total recovery time: ~10s
  (proxy heal ~5s + LLM probe
  + 2s restart + verify)
end note

@enduml
